+    /// Check whether each string starts with `pat`, replacing nulls with `na`.
+    ///
+    /// Matches `pd.Series.str.startswith(pat, na=...)`. When `na` is
+    /// `None` (Rust `None`), nulls propagate as NaN — same as the
